# 💰 Chama Expense Tracker

The **Chama Expense Tracker** is a simple web application that helps users manage group contributions (Chamas), record expenses, calculate balances, and track individual member activity. It allows adding contributions with descriptions, logging expenses, searching for members, and removing entries — all displayed in a clean, interactive interface.

## 🖼️ Preview

![App Screenshot](https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1508780709619-79562169bc64?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1350&q=80)

## ✨ Features

- 📥 Add member contributions with descriptions
- 💸 Record expenses that deduct from the total balance
- 📊 Real-time calculation of total contributions, total expenses, and balance
- 🧍 View all contributing members
- 🔍 Search for a member by name
- ❌ Remove a member or delete an expense
- 🌄 Stylish, responsive UI with background image using Tailwind CSS
- 🔄 Data persists using JSON server (`db.json`)

---

## ⚙️ Technologies Used

- HTML5
- CSS (Tailwind CSS)
- JavaScript (ES6)
- JSON Server (for mock backend)

